            "detailed_description": "<a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.twitch.tv/videos/143938807\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  ><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/378540/extras/TheSurge_Twitch_DevSession_616x200_Replay.jpg?t=1539081140\" ></a><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/378540/extras/TS-Steam-Welcome-to-Creo.png?t=1539081140\" ><br>A catastrophic event has knocked you out during the first day on the job… you wake up equipped with a heavy-grade exoskeleton, in a destroyed section of the complex. Robots gone haywire, insane augmented co-workers and rogue AI - everything wants you dead.<br><br>Defy deadly enemies and huge bosses in tight, visceral melee combat. Target and slice specific limbs off your foes, with a next-gen loot system where you loot what you dismember. Equip, upgrade and craft new weapons and armors sliced from enemies, and make yourself stronger through a fresh take on leveling-up.<br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/378540/extras/TS-Steam-FOND.png?t=1539081140\" >",
